directories.name: 9716621_implicitly_pipelined_tcgen05_instructions
directories.description: Instructions `tcgen05.commit` and `tcgen05.wait` are implicitly pipelined with respect to previously issued `tcgen05.{mma,cp,shift}` and `tcgen05.{ld,st}` instructions respectively that they track from the same thread.

files.title: Overview
files.summary: The asynchronous `tcgen05` operations may execute and complete in a different order than they were issued. However, some specific pairs of the asynchronous `tcgen05` instructions form `tcgen05` pipelines, where in the two asynchronous operations are guaranteed to execute in the same order as the ...
